<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>10745</hymn_number>
<title>mrạḥmk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 mrạḥmk yạ ạ̹lhy̱ ktẖyrẗ jdạaⁿ

[V2]
 mrạḥmk yạ ạ̹lhy lạ yḥṣy̱ lhạ ʿddạaⁿ

[V3]
 qṭrạt ạlạ̉mṭạr mʿdwdẗ byn ydyk

[V4]
 ạ̉yḍạaⁿ rml ạlbḥạr kạỷn qdạm ʿynyk

[V5]
 km bạlạ̉ktẖr kẖṭạyạy wậtẖạmy qdạmk

[V6]
 wmạ ṣnʿth ydạy ẓạhr klh ạ̉mạmk

[V7]
 kẖṭạyạ ṣbạ jhly yạ rb lạ tdẖkrhạ

[V8]
 wlạ ttạml ậtẖạmy yạ ạ̹lhy ạ̹trkhạ

[V9]
 lạ tḥb mwt ạlkẖạṭy̱ʾ krjwʿh ạ̹lyk

[V10]
 yạ rb ạ̹qbl ṭlbty rjʿt wtbt ạ̹lyk

[V11]
 ạlʿsẖạr ạ̹kẖtrth wạlkẖạṭỷẗ gẖfrt lhạ

[V12]
 wạllṣ qd dẖkrth rḥmtk lạ nhạyh lhạ

[V13]
 wạ̉nạ ạlkẖạṭy̱ʾ ạ̉yḍạaⁿ yạ rb ʿlmny

[V14]
 lky ạ̉ṣnʿ twbẗ yạ rb lạ trdẖlny

[V15]
 rdnạ yạ ạllh lkẖlạṣk lạ̉nk ṣạlḥ wrḥym

[V16]
 ạ̹ṣnʿ mʿnạ kṣlạḥk yạ rb wnjnạ</lyrics>
</song>